Package: OssaNMA
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the Optimal Sample Size Allocation of a New Two-Arm Trial when Analyzing with a Existing Network Meta-analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fangshu", "Ye", , "fye@iastate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of functions calculating the minimum total sample size needed to achieve a pre-specified power or the optimal allocation for each treatment group with a fixed total sample size to maximize the power.
